      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "星見市で行った事務所総出のスペシャルライブも\n四人になったリズノワのライブも……",
      "startTime": 154.9713736856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんが星見市のライブで琴乃さんと一緒に\nあの麻奈さんの曲を歌ったことも……大切な経験です",
      "startTime": 161.4216101772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "だから星見市は外せないよね、って\nこころがこの場所を推したんです",
      "startTime": 168.804707019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
